      <title>Blue Owl 牵头的私人债务集团收购 Pluralsight</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/blue-owl-led-private-debt-group-takes-ownership-of-pluralsight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私人信贷机构已同意收购 Pluralsight Inc. 的所有权，三年前 Vista Equity Partners 收购了这家教育软件公司，这是私募股权投资迅速瓦解的体现。]]></description>
